data.description:
Holiday $PECIAL!! Open House Saturday, December 16, 2023, 1-3 p.m.
Charming Colonial 4 BR/2.5 bath two-story Chesterfield home in sought after Highcroft Estates. Great living space with some hardwood floors, newer stainless appliances, wood burning fireplace, French doors & convenient main floor laundry. Walkout from Kitchen & Great Room to an expansive deck & fenced in private yard for the ultimate entertainment! Large master suite with sitting area & nice bathroom en-suite. Finished walk-out basement for additional living area or office. Conveniently located near Shopping, Restaurants, schools and a community pool within walking distance. Quick access to Highway 40. Newer roof, furnace and water heater, but the property needs some face-lifting. Great floor plan, square footage with so much potential! A Parkway School District home with great bones! Investors this is an amazing opportunity to expand your portfolio and make a wonderful investment!
